  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">Contribution to the Cotton Reform Multi-Donors Trust Fund of the World Bank</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">The World Bank led multi-donor trust fund will contribute to a sustainable cotton reform by thoroughly monitoring child and forced labour during cotton harvest, building the capacities of relevant authorities in terms of international&#xA0;standards and legislaion, raising awareness of the population and the stakeholders&apos; groups involved in cotton&#xA0;picking. This will feed into policy dialogue with the Government and eventually eradicate this harmful practice for the rural population.</narrative>
  </description>
